"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2485249-turkish-shooter-yusuf-dikec-dubbed-john-wick-of-the-olympics-for-viral-performance\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"DE The 51-year-old's casual approach and natural skill earn him a silver medal and internet fame.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 98, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 51-year-old's casual approach\", \"from\": 3, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"natural skill\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 54}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 78}, {\"ngram\": \"internet fame\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 96}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known as the \\\"John Wick\\\" of the Olympics, 51-year-old Turkish shooter Yusuf Dikec has gone viral for his performance in the mixed pairs 10-meter air pistol event at the 2024 games.\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.9999085424683034, \"rank\": 7.703925591597577e-05, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"John Wick\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 123}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed pairs\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"10-meter air pistol event\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 games\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Representing Turkey, Dikec secured a silver medal with his relaxed and laid-back approach, which has captivated social media.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9867075725056988, \"rank\": 0.009191932994991658, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"his relaxed and laid-back approach\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The comparison to the John Wick film series, featuring Keanu Reeves as a retired assassin, highlights Dikec's cool demeanor in a high-stakes environment.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keanu_Reeves\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0919891084709404e-27, \"text\": \"Keanu Reeves\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keanu_Reeves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keanu_Reeves\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The comparison\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"the John Wick film series\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"a retired assassin\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec's cool demeanor\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-stakes environment\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike his competitors, who wore specialized gear such as glasses and ear protection, Dikec casually stood with one hand in his pocket, effortlessly hitting his targets and winning second place.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his competitors\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"specialized gear\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"glasses\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"ear protection\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"one hand\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"his pocket\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"his targets\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"second place\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with Turkish media outlet Milat Gazetesi, Dikec explained his unconventional style: \\\"I did not need special equipment.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"Turkish media outlet Milat Gazetesi\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"his unconventional style\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"special equipment\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a natural, a natural shooter.\\\"\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a natural, a natural shooter\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers quickly turned Dikec's performance into a meme, celebrating his nonchalant attitude.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Viewers\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec's performance\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"a meme\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"his nonchalant attitude\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some popular tweets include comments like, \\\"Looks like he was taking a walk around the park then decided to drop by for the Olympics,\\\" and \\\"i know a trained assassin when i see one.\\\"\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some popular tweets\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"a walk\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"the park\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"a trained assassin\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dikec's effortless skill and viral fame have made him a standout at the 2024 Olympics, with fans eagerly sharing and commenting on his unique approach to the sport.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dikec's effortless skill\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"viral fame\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"his unique approach\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"COMMENTS Comments\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"topic\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, please see ourComments FAQ This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, redistributed or derived from.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"ourComments\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"FAQ\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"This material\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise stated, all content is copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all content\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"The Express Tribune\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1714}]}]}"